fix: inventory name clipping, carousel item overflow, tiny Ahrefs logo

- Inventory names: single-line ellipsis instead of 2-line clamp, prevents clipping on narrow mobile cards
- Carousel: roller height 130 -> 168px, item height 130 -> 138px so items fit fully with border + glow
- Specials: drop transform: scale (was clipping at top/bottom), keep stronger box-shadow glow and thicker bottom rarity bar (6px)
- Ahrefs SVG: add viewBox, remove fixed 16x16 width/height so it scales to fill the crest container
- Crest img: switch to width/height 100% with object-fit contain for consistent scaling across SVGs
